TopicTitle: Missing collider on Dres Equatorial mountains

Articles.Content:
OS: Win 10

Kerbal Version: 0.1.1.0

I wanted to land on the equator on Dres and just fell straight through the mountains there.

I don't see a way to upload an image, but it's on the brightly colored side of Dres right between the two big craters on the equator. North west of the 2 scar like canyons

Anyway props to the devs. The first patch really improved things a lot already.
